<lb n="0770a21" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 501</head>
<lb n="0770a22" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說沙曷比丘功德經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0770a23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0770a24" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">西晉沙門<note n="0770012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（釋）＋法炬【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（釋）＋法炬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770012"><lem wit="【大】">法炬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">釋法炬</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0770a25" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0770a2501">聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。時
<lb n="0770a26" ed="T"/>與千二百五十比丘菩薩萬人。時須耶國有
<lb n="0770a27" ed="T"/>貧人。行賃剃小兒頭。所剃者皆約。到麥熟
<lb n="0770a28" ed="T"/>當各雇麥一斛。適別未遠。道逢<note n="0770013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">故＝雇【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故＝雇【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770013"><lem wit="【大】">故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雇</rdg></app>人。將其
<lb n="0770a29" ed="T"/>還求麥。欲以取酒飲之。遍求無以麥還者。於
<pb n="0770b" id="T14.0501.0770b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0770b01" ed="T"/>是便起恚意言。願我壽終後。作大神龍。當
<lb n="0770b02" ed="T"/>陷此國後壽終。魂神遂還作龍。其國中歷
<lb n="0770b03" ed="T"/>年風雨不時。五穀毀敗佛念此國人民飢饉。
<lb n="0770b04" ed="T"/>即遣沙曷比丘往化之。龍見比丘。往即興惡
<lb n="0770b05" ed="T"/>意。欲敗國及殺沙曷比丘。沙曷便變化&CB00425;覆
<lb n="0770b06" ed="T"/>蓋一國。龍雨之謂國已沒。比丘以佛威神
<lb n="0770b07" ed="T"/>令龍見。人民安隱如故。龍復興恚意下雪。比
<lb n="0770b08" ed="T"/>丘以&CB00425;受之雪極比丘以手掃之。著一處如
<lb n="0770b09" ed="T"/>山。比丘乃入龍室。龍即出比丘復出。龍入
<lb n="0770b10" ed="T"/>比丘復入。如是若干輩。龍極乃止。長跪問言。
<lb n="0770b11" ed="T"/>卿何<note n="0770014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">等神＝神等【元】【明】</note><app n="0770014"><lem wit="【大】">等神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">神等</rdg></app>。惱我如此。比丘言。吾是佛弟子。
<lb n="0770b12" ed="T"/>龍言。我欲自歸於卿。比丘答<note n="0770015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔言〕－【聖】</note><app n="0770015"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>。吾有大師。
<lb n="0770b13" ed="T"/>佛三界最尊。卿當自歸之。龍言。佛在何所。
<lb n="0770b14" ed="T"/>報言。佛在舍衛國。龍言。乞逐道人去。比丘
<lb n="0770b15" ed="T"/>言。欲去者善。便內龍著<note n="0770016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">笥＝笱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">笥＝笱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770016"><lem wit="【大】">笥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">笱</rdg></app>中。人民見比丘
<lb n="0770b16" ed="T"/>取龍如是。<note n="0770017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">皆＝有【宮】</note><app n="0770017"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">有</rdg></app>歡喜問言。道人是何等大神。
<lb n="0770b17" ed="T"/>降伏國患。告言吾是佛弟子。人民問言。佛
<lb n="0770b18" ed="T"/>可得見不。答言。欲得見佛且<note n="0770018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">待＝須【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0770018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">待＝須【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0770018"><lem wit="【大】">待</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">須</rdg></app>。吾<note n="0770019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">還＝運【宮】</note><app n="0770019"><lem wit="【大】">還</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">運</rdg></app>時
<lb n="0770b19" ed="T"/>日向中道<note n="0770020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遇＝過【宮】</note><app n="0770020"><lem wit="【大】">遇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">過</rdg></app>分衛。人<note n="0770021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔民〕－【聖】</note><app n="0770021"><lem wit="【大】">民</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>或與飯者。與酒者
<lb n="0770b20" ed="T"/>比丘受而食飲之。致酒醉<note n="0770022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遇＝過【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遇＝過【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770022"><lem wit="【大】">遇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">過</rdg></app>樹下臥。龍&CB00425;袈
<lb n="0770b21" ed="T"/>裟。各在一處。佛<note n="0770023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">時＝笑【宮】</note><app n="0770023"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">笑</rdg></app>笑。五色光出。阿難<note n="0770024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">正＝整【明】</note><app n="0770024"><lem wit="【大】">正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">整</rdg></app>
<lb n="0770b22" ed="T"/>衣服。叉手白佛言。佛不妄笑。笑必有意。佛
<lb n="0770b23" ed="T"/>告阿難。汝為見沙曷比丘不。阿難言。不見。佛
<lb n="0770b24" ed="T"/>言。今在彼樹下醉臥。時千二百五十比丘。菩
<lb n="0770b25" ed="T"/>薩萬人。各相與語言。沙曷比丘已得阿羅漢。
<lb n="0770b26" ed="T"/>何以復醉臥。佛知諸人意有疑。因說四事。一
<lb n="0770b27" ed="T"/>者阿羅漢。不三昧不得知。二者不得便現神
<lb n="0770b28" ed="T"/>足。三者不<note n="0770025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得＝張【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0770025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得＝張【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0770025"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">張</rdg></app>強勸人分衛。四者身中尚有
<lb n="0770b29" ed="T"/>蟲。阿羅漢以是四事不及佛。時萬菩薩。皆
<pb n="0770c" id="T14.0501.0770c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0770c01" ed="T"/>迴意欲向羅漢。佛遣目<note n="0770026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">犍＝揵【聖】</note><app n="0770026"><lem wit="【大】">犍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">揵</rdg></app>連。往到沙曷比
<lb n="0770c02" ed="T"/>丘所。&CB00330;之攝龍來。龍以頭面。為佛作禮。佛
<lb n="0770c03" ed="T"/>便為說宿<note n="0770027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔命〕－【聖】</note><app n="0770027"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>本末。龍心即解。受五戒奉行
<lb n="0770c04" ed="T"/>十善。即得須陀洹道。為佛作禮而去。佛時
<lb n="0770c05" ed="T"/>說沙曷比丘功德微妙。阿難叉手啟佛言。沙
<lb n="0770c06" ed="T"/>曷比丘飲酒醉臥。而佛說其功德微妙乃爾。
<lb n="0770c07" ed="T"/>佛告阿難。阿羅漢不復飢渴。用三事故。現
<lb n="0770c08" ed="T"/>醉臥耳。一者佛欲開化菩薩意。二者不欲逆
<lb n="0770c09" ed="T"/>布施家意。三者恐諸弟子未得道者。飲酒多
<lb n="0770c10" ed="T"/>失故。以此至戒撿之。沙曷比丘雖飲酒是為
<lb n="0770c11" ed="T"/>不醉。諸菩薩四輩弟子。聞佛說是。皆起整
<lb n="0770c12" ed="T"/>衣服。為佛作禮。沙曷比丘更前長跪白佛言。
<lb n="0770c13" ed="T"/>須耶越國王人民欲見。<note n="0770028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（佛）＋佛【聖】</note><app n="0770028"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">佛佛</rdg></app>默然受之。沙曷比
<lb n="0770c14" ed="T"/>丘。即承佛教。如彈指頃。還到須耶越國。國
<lb n="0770c15" ed="T"/>王人民見比丘。皆歡喜有作禮者。有跪者。但
<lb n="0770c16" ed="T"/>叉手者。沙曷比丘告言。佛明日當來到。此
<lb n="0770c17" ed="T"/>王聞佛當來大歡喜。豫於四衢道。掃灑廣施
<lb n="0770c18" ed="T"/>帳幔。佛明日與千二百五十比丘俱。豫行空
<lb n="0770c19" ed="T"/>中。<note n="0770029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔皆〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0770029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔皆〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0770029"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>有自然蓮華。<note n="0770030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">奉＝捧【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0770030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奉＝捧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0770030"><lem wit="【大】">奉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">捧</rdg></app>佛足下。王及<note n="0770031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">臣＝人【明】</note><app n="0770031"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">人</rdg></app>民。
<lb n="0770c20" ed="T"/>皆以<note n="0770032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">華香＝香華【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">華香＝香華【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770032"><lem wit="【大】">華香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">香華</rdg></app>。出城迎佛。五體投地。稽首為禮。
<lb n="0770c21" ed="T"/>佛及比丘。到宮即有自然師子座。布以綩綖。
<lb n="0770c22" ed="T"/>七寶華蓋。五色交絡。<note n="0770033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">王＝五【明】</note><app n="0770033"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">五</rdg></app>施設供養。手自斟
<lb n="0770c23" ed="T"/>酌。飯畢行<note n="0770034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02900;＝盥【宋】</note><note n="0770034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02900;＝盥【宋】【CB】</note><app n="0770034"><lem wit="【CBETA】【麗】" resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="K20n0851_p1197a14">盥</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB02900;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">盥</rdg></app>水祝願。佛為王及人民。說龍
<lb n="0770c24" ed="T"/>本末。王與人民心解。即受五戒行十善。或
<lb n="0770c25" ed="T"/>得須陀洹者。斯陀含。阿那含。阿羅漢者。不
<lb n="0770c26" ed="T"/>可<note n="0770035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">稱＝勝【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">稱＝勝【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770035"><lem wit="【大】">稱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">勝</rdg></app>數。佛說經竟。四輩弟子。天龍鬼神。<note n="0770036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">歡喜奉行＝皆歡喜作禮而去【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0770036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歡喜奉行＝皆歡喜作禮而去【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0770036"><lem wit="【大】">歡
<lb n="0770c27" ed="T"/>喜奉行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">皆歡喜作禮而去</rdg></app>。</p></div1>
<lb n="0770c28" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0770037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛說〕－【聖】</note><app n="0770037"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>沙曷比丘功德經</jhead><note n="0770038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光明皇后願文【聖】</note></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>